Usage: setWhatIfClockLatency [-help] <blackBoxCellName>
                             [-clockFrom <clockPortName>] [-genConstr <value>]
                             [-init <value>] [-new <value>]

-help                          # Prints out the command usage
<blackBoxCellName>             # name of the blackbox or blackblob cell
                               # (string, required)
-clockFrom <clockPortName>     # Specifies the name of the clock input port
                               # (string, optional)
-genConstr <value>             # Specifies the latency to consider in the
                               # what-if timing constraints generation
                               # (float, optional)
-init <value>                  # Specifies the current clock insertion delay
                               # value (float, optional)
-new <value>                   # Specifies the new clock latency value
                               # (float, optional)